# Execute Runtime

- `POST /v1/integrations/execute` enforcement must call `evaluate_policy(...)` before runtime execution.
- Keep allowlist, spoof prevention, and PHI/admin policy gates in policy engine; avoid duplicate inline policy branches.
- AI formatter checks are informational and must not change execute allow/deny outcome.
- Preserve existing runtime semantics when refactoring policy checks (no hidden behavior changes).
